{% block form %}

    <h1 class="govuk-heading-l">
      You cannot help someone to apply if someone else has authority over their benefits or financial affairs
    </h1>

    {% if locale == 'NI' %}
    <p class="govuk-body">
      If someone has been appointed to make decisions for the person you are helping, for example an Enduring Power of Attorney (EPA),
      that person will need to complete the application for Attendance Allowance.
    </p>
    {% else %}
    <p class="govuk-body">
      If someone has been appointed to make decisions for the person you are helping, for example a power of attorney,
      that person will need to complete the application for Attendance Allowance.
    </p>
    {% endif %}

    <p class="govuk-body">
      This is because we need additional information about them. This claim will be delayed if we do not have this information.
    </p>

{% endblock %}

